Impossible Humans - The Unexpected Happening - Teaser 2

IMPOSSIBLE HUMANS - THE UNEXPECTED HAPPENING Submission page (DECEMBER 22 2015 to JANUARY 21 2016 (23:59 GMT+1) http://neweramuseum.org/ihuh-entries/ "LABELS ARE FOR JARS. NOT FOR PEOPLE " (Andy Warhol) A visionary performance of contemporary art, music and new visual arts, where the Pollock Project's jazz meets the imaginative world of the artists from the New Era Museum (NEM).
